videos.headline: Liberty takes early lead on 22-yard TD
videos.description: Frankie Hickson gives Liberty an early 7-0 lead on a 22-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: New Mexico State goes up on 10-yard TD
videos.description: Anthony Muse pulls in a touchdown catch to give New Mexico State a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Gibson bounces off defender then breaks loose for 66-yard TD
videos.description: Christian Gibson finds the end zone for a 66-yard score, extending New Mexico State's lead 49-35.
